HEADWORD: Disclose
<hw>Dis*close"</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Disclosure.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Shak. Young.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Disclosed</ent>⟦br⟧
